org.fudgemsg
Interface FudgeStreamWriter

All Superinterfaces:
java.io.Closeable, java.io.Flushable
All Known Implementing Classes:
FudgeDataOutputStreamWriter, FudgeXMLStreamWriter
public interface FudgeStreamWriter
extends java.io.Flushable, java.io.Closeable

Abstract interface for writing Fudge elements to a target. This base can be used to build full Fudge message writers or serialisers to convert Java objects directly to Fudge streams.

Writes a message field.

Parameters:
ordinal - the ordinal index of the field, or null to omit.

fieldValue - value of the field
